0. Overview & Concepts

	Before we delve into the individual parts of this system, let's take a shot of the big picture. This will provide context for each element below.
	The inTown Project was originally conceived 8 years ago as a social networking platform with a focus on local community building. It has since grown in scope with more emphasis on civic duty and the democratic process, so that now perhaps it will become the first "civil network".
